<section>
	<div id="slideshow"></div>
</section>
<section>
	<h1>First time here?</h1>
	<p>Online Drum Teacher is a learning resource for aspiring drummers and advanced drummers alike. We're excited to bring you written lessons, video lessons and a regularly updated blog all for free!</p>
	<p>For those who are looking to take the next step in advancing their percussion abilities, we offer premium content to members of the site. A large collection of videos and written lessons are available only to members.</p>
	<p>Check out the store page to purchase Curtis Cooper's books and visit the webcam lessons page to learn more about 1 on 1 lessons with Curtis via Skype, oovoo, etc.</p>
</section>
<section>
	<div class="widget blog">
		<div class="category_title">
			<%= link_to "Blog", blogposts_path, class: "cat_box_blog" %>
		</div>
		<ul class="category_box">
			<% if @blogposts.nil? %>
				There are no blog entries.
			<% else %>
				<% @blogposts.each_with_index do |blogpost, index| %>
					<% if index < 3 %>
						<li>
							<%= link_to raw('<span>#{blogpost.title}</span>') %>
						</li>
					<% end %>
				<% end %>
			<% end %>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<div class="clear"></div>
</section>

